<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0628001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0628001">XII. Lokasandarśana parivarta.</note>
<note n="0628002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0628002">〔之一〕－【元】</note>
<note n="0628003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0628003">今＝令【元】</note>
